<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Document</title>
	<style type="text/css">
		*{
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
		}
		header{
			position: relative;
		}
		.left{
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			left: 0;
			width: 120px;
			height: 60px;
			background-color: #b80964;
		}
		.main{
			width: 100%;
			height: 60px;
			background-color: orange;
			padding: 0 120px;
			box-sizing:border-box;
		/*	-webkit-box-sizing:border-box;
			-moz-box-sizing:border-box;
			-ms-box-sizing:border-box;
			-o-box-sizing:border-box;*/
		}
		.right{
			position: absolute;
			top: 0;
			right: 0;
			width: 120px;
			height: 60px;
			background-color: #b80964;
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<div class="left">left</div>
		<div class="main">main</main>
		<div class="right">right</div>
	</header>
</body>
</html>

/*
* 实现两边固定，中间自适应
* 元素设置box-sizing:border-box后，增加padding，实际宽度不会增加，而正常的content-box,实际宽度 = width + padding 
* 与圣杯布局区别：
* 1、圣杯布局是父元素设置padding,而子元素的width:100%等于父元素的可用宽度，从而挤出main区域的位置
* 2、border-box是给main元素设置padding,box-sizing:border-box后，自己内容区域宽度减少
*
******/
